  "text": "I am raw. This will be the last full question of this session. The root of astrology, as you speak it, is one way of perceiving the primal distortions which may be a predicted along a probability, a possibility, lines given the, shall we say, cosmic orientations and configurations at the time of the entrance into the physical, mental complex of the spirit, and at the time of the physical, a mental, a spiritual complex into the illusion. This then has the possibility of suggesting basic areas of distortion. There is no more than this. The part astrology plays is alikened unto that of one root among many.",
